Devastation Orbs

Overview

Profile

A Devastation Orb measures 12 inches in diameter, weighs 10 lbs, and has a solid outer shell.

Capabilities

Regardless of the type of orb, its effect is contained within a sphere with a 1 mile radius. The orb is the sphere’s point of origin. The orb is destroyed after 1 use.

Air Orb. When this orb detonates, it creates a powerful windstorm that lasts for 1 hour.

Earth Orb. When this orb detonates, it subjects the area to the effects of the Earthquake spell for 1 hour.

Fire Orb. When this orb detonates, it creates a intense dry heat wave, wildfire, and can possibly draw volcanic erruption that lasts for 1 hour.

Water Orb. When this orb detonates, it creates a torrential rainstorm, massive flash flooding, wirlpools, and more that lasts for 1 hour.
